{"tha-ap19:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap19:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap19:0.3":"7 Upasenavangantaputtattheraapadana ","tha-ap19:1.1":"“Padumuttaram bhagavantam, ","tha-ap19:1.2":"lokajettham narasabham; ","tha-ap19:1.3":"Pabbharamhi nisidantam, ","tha-ap19:1.4":"upagacchim naruttamam. ","tha-ap19:2.1":"Kanikarapuppham disva, ","tha-ap19:2.2":"vante chetvanaham tada; ","tha-ap19:2.3":"Alankaritva chattamhi, ","tha-ap19:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap19:3.1":"Pindapatanca padasim, ","tha-ap19:3.2":"paramannam subhojanam; ","tha-ap19:3.3":"Buddhena navame tattha, ","tha-ap19:3.4":"samane attha bhojayim. ","tha-ap19:4.1":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","tha-ap19:4.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap19:4.3":"Imina chattadanena, ","tha-ap19:4.4":"paramannapavecchana. ","tha-ap19:5.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap19:5.2":"sampattimanubhossasi; ","tha-ap19:5.3":"Chattimsakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap19:5.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap19:6.1":"Ekavisatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap19:6.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap19:6.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap19:6.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap19:7.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap19:7.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap19:7.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap19:7.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap19:8.1":"Sasane dibbamanamhi, ","tha-ap19:8.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap19:8.3":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap19:8.4":"oraso dhammanimmito. ","tha-ap19:9.1":"Upasenoti namena, ","tha-ap19:9.2":"hessati satthu savako; ","tha-ap19:9.3":"Samantapasadikatta, ","tha-ap19:9.4":"aggatthane thapessati. ","tha-ap19:10.1":"Carimam vattate mayham, ","tha-ap19:10.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap19:10.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap19:10.4":"jetva maram savahinim. ","tha-ap19:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap19:11.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap19:11.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap19:11.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap19:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upaseno vangantaputto thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap19:13.1":"Upasenavangantaputtattherassapadanam sattamam. ","tha-ap19:13.2":"Tatiyabhanavaram. "}